    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s driver, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-Differential Lock, ensuring tactile engagement and linear power delivery to the rear wheels. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and professional reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension remains composed with factory-spec MacPherson struts and a multi-link rear arrangement, though the bushings show standard wear typical of a well-driven example. This is a mechanically robust specimen that prioritizes high-revving performance and analog feedback over concours-level aesthetics.",
